flowchart TD
    A([User runs: license-wizard]) --> LW[License Wizard]
    A -.->|flags| FL([Flags])
    FL -.-> LW
    LW -.->|reads| LC[/License config file/]
    LW -.->|reads license field<br/>composer.json → package.json| PJ[/Project manifests/]

    LW --> M{--verify flag?}

    %% ─── Interactive / generation path ───
    M -->|No| C

    subgraph IO [Input Orchestrator]
        C[Prepare question]
        C --> D[Ask question]
        D --> E[Receive answer<br/>user accepts default or provides value]
        E --> F{more questions?}
        F -->|Yes| C
        F -->|No| OG[Generate options object]
    end

    OG -->|options object| LW
    LW -->|writes| LC
    LW --> G[License is generated]
    G -->|writes license id<br/>to all present manifests| PJ
    G --> H([Done])

    %% ─── Verification path ───
    M -->|Yes| V[Verify]
    V -.->|reads| EL[/Existing LICENSE file/]
    V --> R{License matches config?}
    R -->|Yes| PASS([Pass])
    R -->|No| AG{Auto-generate enabled?}
    AG -->|Yes| G
    AG -->|No| FAIL([Fail])
